[
        {"tag":"Day 1 — The Pain","title":"Why Double-Entry Is Silently Killing Your Business Growth","description":"Every time you copy a number from your invoice to your spreadsheet, you're not just wasting time — you're creating a crack in your data foundation that compounds every single month.","points":["The hidden cost of manual re-entry (it's not just time)","Why \"good enough\" spreadsheets become dangerous at scale","Real stories: month-end chaos that didn't have to happen","The tipping point — when does spreadsheet pain become a business risk?"],"footer":"Awareness Content"},
        {"tag":"Day 2 — The Trend","title":"Smarter, Integrated Systems Are No Longer Just for Enterprise","description":"The shift is already happening. Modern SMBs are discovering that unified business systems — once reserved for large corporations — are now accessible, affordable, and built for teams of any size.","points":["How integrated ERP has democratised in the last 5 years","What \"unified system\" actually means in practice for a 5-50 person team","The three data flows every business must connect: inventory, sales, cash","Why open-source changes the cost and risk equation entirely"],"footer":"Education Content"},
        {"tag":"Day 3 — The Prize","title":"Your Clear Path to a Unified Business — Starting This Month","description":"Stop waiting for the \"right time.\" This post outlines the exact low-risk migration strategy that lets you move to a single source of truth — without disrupting daily operations or hiring a single extra person.","points":["The 3-phase migration that keeps your business running while you upgrade","Real-time stock and cash visibility — what it looks like on day one","How to eliminate month-end chaos for good","Reclaiming 5+ hours per week: what could you build with that time?"],"footer":"Conversion Content"},
        {"tag":"Free Guide — All Three Combined","title":"The Complete Spreadsheet Freedom Playbook","description":"Everything above, plus a practical step-by-step workbook to assess your current setup, plan your migration, and measure success — tailored for business owners, not IT departments.","points":["Self-assessment: Are you ready to ditch spreadsheets?","Migration checklist — 30 day action plan","Questions to ask any ERP vendor before you sign","How to calculate your ROI before you commit to anything"],"footer":"Get It Free Below"}
      ]

[
        {"title":"Week 1 — Assess & Map","description":"Identify every place data lives and every manual re-entry touchpoint. Use our self-assessment worksheet to score your current setup and spot the highest-impact fixes."},
        {"title":"Week 2 — Connect the Core Three","description":"Link your inventory, sales, and cash flows into a single system. Real-time stock visibility and auto-reconciled financials become the new normal — while your business keeps running."},
        {"title":"Week 3 — Eliminate the Chaos","description":"Retire your last spreadsheet. Set up automated month-end reports. Watch data errors drop to zero. This is the week you get 5+ hours back."},
        {"title":"Week 4 — Scale With Confidence","description":"Your business can now grow without back-office headcount growing with it. Use the time and data clarity to make decisions faster — and with confidence in your numbers."}
      ]
